Sequences from peaks with AR and ER detected

Source: R/data.R
ar_er_seq.Rd

The genomic sequences obtained from the ar_er_peaks

Usage

data("ar_er_seq")

Format

An object of class DNAStringSet of length 849.

Details

These sequences represent the sequences obtained from BSgenome.Hsapiens.UCSC.hg19 for thw peaks supplied as ar_er_peaks

Generation of these sequences is documented in system.file("scripts/ar_er_peaks.R", package = "motifTestR")

Examples

data("ar_er_seq")
